{"tid":601976,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（周街連登仔）每七個香港人有一個百萬富翁","createTime":"2018-03-22T15:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T16:03:01.000Z","uid":100256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1cece67fac7e284b5386bec0d899b84609590f2b","tid":601976,"uid":100256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:55:32.000Z","msg":"花旗銀行發表香港千萬富翁調查報告，去年本港擁有一千萬港元或以上流動資產的富裕人士，按年增加15%，達到6.8萬名。另外，本港去年新增20多萬名百萬富翁至100.8萬名，按年亦增加15%。<br />\n<br />\n千萬富翁的投資資產組合中，現金比例仍維持約36%，39%富翁擁有海外物業。38%富翁預期本港樓價繼續升，而2016年只有25%富翁預期樓價上升。<br />\n<br />\n調查在去年9月至11月，以電話形式訪問逾4100名香港富裕人士，並在港街訪200名內地富裕人士。發現兩地的富裕人士資產分布相若，當中逾70%總資產都投放在物業。<br />\n<br />\n不過，本港富裕人士有過半的財富來自薪酬收入，其次是經營生意，而內地富裕人士則主要靠經營生意，其次是投資。<br />\n<br />\n調查亦發現，受僱的富裕人士當中，內地人較港人更愛創業。另外，較多香港富裕人士最不滿本港居住環境及教育制度，內地富裕人士則對內地醫療制度最為關注。"},{"pid":"014fe979ffcdcf0ae00f94712d07a536af31d97e","tid":601976,"uid":100256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:56:41.000Z","msg":"連登仔係咪每七個只有一個唔係百萬富翁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c154c61b28d5f1993dd2a0ed2c85b8dd05cd18ab","tid":601976,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:57:37.000Z","msg":"將十年前嘅百萬富翁急凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後而家解凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a87223e2f7c1638814cd3b5c02cd4dc11625b35","tid":601976,"uid":153976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"百萬＝富翁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b528bf0e0c57a05c66973ad53173a65208d658fe","tid":601976,"uid":100256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a87223e2f7c1638814cd3b5c02cd4dc11625b35","tid":601976,"uid":153976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"百萬＝富翁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T16:03:01.000Z","msg":"流動資金 算唔差啦<br />\n知你過千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}